    &lt;x_fitbit_fun_with_fitbit_labs action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"&gt;
        &lt;code_sample/&gt;
        &lt;details&gt;&lt;![CDATA[&lt;h1&gt;Register application in fitbit&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Create a new application for your account in fitbit. Information &lt;br /&gt; &lt;a href="https://dev.fitbit.com/apps/new" rel="nofollow"&gt;https://dev.fitbit.com/apps/new&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 12.0pt;"&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Application Name: &lt;strong&gt;CreatorCon workshop&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Application Website: https://&lt;strong&gt;[instance].service-now.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Organization: &lt;strong&gt;creatorCon workshop&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Organization Website: https://&lt;strong&gt;[instance].service-now.com&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Oauth Authentication Type: &lt;strong&gt;server&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Callback URL: &lt;a href="https://[instance].service-now.com/oauth_redirect.do" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;strong&gt;https://[instance].service-now.com/oauth_redirect.do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Default Access Type: &lt;strong&gt;Read &amp;amp; Write&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Save and capture your info you will need this in ServiceNow&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will need this information in the next step&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #343333;"&gt;OAuth 2.0 Client ID : ____________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #343333;"&gt;Client (Consumer) Secret: ________________&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #343333;"&gt;OAuth 2.0: Authorization URI: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.fitbit.com/oauth2/authorize" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10.5pt;"&gt;https://www.fitbit.com/oauth2/authorize&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style="color: #343333;"&gt;OAuth 2.0: Access/Refresh Token Request URI: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;a href="https://api.fitbit.com/oauth2/token" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10.5pt;"&gt;https://api.fitbit.com/oauth2/token&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h1&gt;Register your new Application in ServiceNow&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;System OAuth/Application Registry&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;New - &lt;a href="https://dev11095.service-now.com/wizard_view.do?sys_action&amp;#61;sysverb_wizard_ans&amp;amp;WIZARD:action&amp;#61;follow&amp;amp;wiz_referring_url&amp;#61;oauth_entity_list.do?sys_id&amp;#61;-1&amp;#64;99&amp;#64;sys_target&amp;#61;oauth_entity&amp;#64;99&amp;#64;sysparm_ck&amp;#61;4cc88f820faede007700943be1050e845e5c04a16f27f4f7c48a98c569ba4a118a5cf560&amp;#64;99&amp;#64;sysparm_fixed_query&amp;#61;&amp;#64;99&amp;#64;sysparm_group_sort&amp;#61;&amp;#64;99&amp;#64;sysparm_parent&amp;#61;2c7cab53d7232100f20bc8170e61036b&amp;#64;99&amp;#64;sysparm_query&amp;#61;type%3dclient%5eORtype%3doauth_provider&amp;#64;99&amp;#64;sysparm_target&amp;#61;&amp;#64;99&amp;#64;sysparm_view&amp;#61;&amp;amp;wiz_collection_key&amp;#61;&amp;amp;wiz_collectionID&amp;#61;&amp;amp;wiz_collection&amp;#61;&amp;amp;wiz_collection_related_field&amp;#61;&amp;amp;wiz_view&amp;#61;&amp;amp;wiz_action&amp;#61;sysverb_new&amp;amp;sys_id&amp;#61;79ce2f53d7232100f20bc8170e610361&amp;amp;sysparm_query&amp;#61;type&amp;#61;client%5eORtype&amp;#61;oauth_provider&amp;amp;sysparm_target&amp;#61;&amp;amp;sys_target&amp;#61;oauth_entity" rel="nofollow"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 10.0pt; color: #278efc;"&gt;Connect to a third party OAuth Provider&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: &lt;strong&gt;fitbitOauth&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Accessible from: &lt;strong&gt;All application Scope&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Client ID: &lt;strong&gt;Value from fitbit&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Client Secret: &lt;strong&gt;Value From fitbit App&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;OAuth API Script: &lt;strong&gt;OAuthUtil&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Active: &lt;strong&gt;True&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Authorization URL: &lt;strong&gt;https://www.fitbit.com/oauth2/authorize &lt;br /&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;Token URL:  &lt;strong&gt;https://api.fitbit.com/oauth2/token&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br /&gt; Default Grant Type: &lt;strong&gt;Authorization Code&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;]]&gt;&lt;/details&gt;
